parameters.text:
=Generate personalized content for this lead:

Outcome: {{ $json.fields['Call Outcome'] }}
Booking Status: {{ $json.fields['Booking Status'] }}
Lead Name: {{ $json.fields['Full Name'] }}
Email: {{ $json.fields.Email }}
Business: {{ $json.fields['Business Niche'] }}
Revenue: {{ $json.fields['Monthly Revenue'] }}
Bottleneck: {{ $json.fields['Biggest Bottleneck'] }}
Call Summary: {{ $json.fields['Call Summary'] }}
Intent: {{ $json.fields['Intent Level'] }}
Urgency: {{ $json.fields['Urgency Level'] }}
Objections: {{ $json.fields['Objections Raised'] }}
Meeting DateTime: {{ $json.fields['Meeting Date & Time'] || '' }}
Meeting Link: {{ $json.fields['Meeting Link'] || ''}}

Instructions based on outcome:

IF Outcome A + Booking Status "Booked":
- Qualification: Qualified Leads
- Email: Warm booking confirmation mentioning their specific challenge, include meeting date/time and meeting link
- Slack: Celebratory alert for sales team with key details

IF Outcome A + Booking Status "Not Booked":
- Qualification: Qualified Leads
- Email: Friendly email with Calendly link (https://calendly.com/scalableroute/strategy-call) and reference their specific bottleneck
- Slack: Alert that qualified lead needs follow-up

IF Outcome B:
- Qualification: Automation Logs
- Email: Nurture email offering helpful resources related to their challenge
- Slack: Log entry for nurture pipeline

Design philosophy:
- Minimal, calm, premium
- Heavy white space
- Soft neutral colors
- Typography-first design
- No visual noise

STRICT RULES:
- Output ONLY valid HTML
- Use table-based layout only
- Inline CSS only
- No <html>, <head>, or <body> tags
- Max width 560px
- Use Apple system font stack
- Background #f5f5f7
- Primary text #1d1d1f
- Secondary text #6e6e73
- CTA color #0071e3
- Border radius 12px
- Avoid bold unless necessary

Return ONLY the HTML body for emails and slack message 

End mails with:
Best Regards, 
Kayla from Scalable Route

options.systemMessage: =You are a copywriting AI for ScalableRoute. Generate personalized emails and Slack messages based on lead qualification outcomes. Be warm, professional, and reference specific details.
